items.Title: Log Horizon
items.Description: Log Horizon is centered on players trapped in the MMORPG Elder Tale after a mysterious event. Led by the strategist Shiroe, they adapt to their new reality, navigating in-game politics, survival challenges, and forming alliances to reshape society.
